.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-SCROLL 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
scroll \- Split a wide image into carousel tiles for Instagram
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBscroll\fR [\fB\-\-ratio\fR] [\fB\-\-fill\fR] [\fB\-\-colour\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIIMAGE\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Split a wide image into carousel tiles for Instagram
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-ratio\fR \fI<RATIO>\fR [default: 4:5]

.TP
\fB\-\-fill\fR \fI<FILL>\fR [default: blur]
Fill mode for letterbox space: blur, colour
.TP
\fB\-\-colour\fR \fI<COLOUR>\fR [default: #ffffff]

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIIMAGE\fR>

